# Validation & testing (BuildY)

## Routine checks

```bash
bun run verify
```

Runs: **`templ generate`** → **`build:css`** → **`lint:ui8px`** → **`validate:aria`** → **`go test ./...`**

## Go render tests

Add **`Test*_wireframeRenders`** in `internal/views` for critical surfaces (app shell, home) so layout/mobile sheet/theme/locale markup regress without a browser. See `wireframe_render_test.go`.

## CSS validator

Deferred until brand polish; Tailwind output is not a strict W3C CSS gate in the wireframe phase.

## Coordination

- **`buildy-atomic-ui8px.mdc`** — lint scope, no raw tags, no custom CSS classes
- **`buildy-aria.mdc`** — manifest + `data-ui8kit` contract
- **`buildy-fixtures-data.mdc`** — sensible strings for screen readers
